[{"title":"C++函数","date":"2020-05-27T11:06:13.000Z","path":"20202020/505/927/C++函数/","content":"<p>函数是一组一起执行一个任务的语句。每个C++程序至少有一个函数，即main()函数。</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>函数的定义：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">返回类型 函数名(参数列表)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ...</span><br><span class=\"line\">    函数体;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ...</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><strong>返回类型</strong>：一个函数可以返回一个值，返回类型是函数返回的值的数据类型。有些函数执行所需的操作但并不返回值，这种情况下函数的返回类型为void。</p>\n<p><strong>函数名称</strong>：这是函数的实际名称。</p>\n<p><strong>参数</strong>：当函数被调用的时候，向参数传递一个值，这个值被称为实际参数。参数列表包括函数参数的类型、顺序、数量。函数可以没有参数。</p>\n<p><strong>函数主体：</strong>函数主体即一组定义函数执行任务的语句。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//函数定义，计算出三个数中的最大值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">max</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b,<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> c)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (a &gt; b) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (a &gt; c) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tresult = a;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tresult = c;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (b &gt; c) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tresult = b;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tresult = c;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>函数的声明</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">返回类型 函数名(参数列表);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>函数声明会告诉编译器函数名称以及如何调用函数，函数的实际主体可以单独定义，并不一定要和main()函数在同一个cpp文件中。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//函数声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">max</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b,<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> c)</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>函数的调用</p>\n<p>调用函数时，传递所需参数，如果函数返回一个值，则可以存储返回值，例如：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> num1 = <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> num2 = <span class=\"number\">20</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> num3 = <span class=\"number\">15</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"comment\">//函数调用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> max_num = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(num1, num2, num3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"a,b,c中最大的数为:\"</span> &lt;&lt; max_num &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tsystem(<span class=\"string\">\"pause\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>如上max()函数所定义的result（int类型）。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>实参和形参的区别</p>\n<p>函数的本质也就是根据不同的参数产生不同的返回值（一些函数不需参数也可以产生返回值）。而C++程序中会出现两种参数，一种是在函数定义处，另一种是在函数调用处，这两种参数是有区别的，前者称为形参后者称为实参。</p>\n<p><strong>形参（形式参数）</strong></p>\n<p>在函数的定义时给出的参数可以看作是一个占位符，他<font color=\"red\">没有数据，只能等到函数被调用时接收传递进来的数据</font>，所以称为形式参数，简称形参。</p>\n<p><strong>实参（实际参数）</strong></p>\n<p>在函数的调用时给出的参数<font color=\"red\">包含了实实在在的数据。会被函数内部代码使用</font>，所以称为实际参数，简称实参。</p>\n<p><strong>实参和形参的区别和联系</strong></p>\n<p>a.形参只有在函数被调用时才会分配内存，调用结束后立即释放内存。</p>\n<p>b.实参在进行函数调用时必须有确定的值，以便把这些值传送给形参，所以在函数调用前实参必须有确定的值。</p>\n<p>c.实参和形参在数量上、类型上、顺序上必须严格一直，否则会发生“类型不匹配”的错误。</p>\n<p>d.函数调用中发生的数据传递是单向的，只能把实参的值传送给形参，而不能把形参的值传送给实参。因此在函数调用过程，形参的变化并不影响实参。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">sum</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> m, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (i = m + <span class=\"number\">1</span>; i &lt;= n; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        m += i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> m;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a, b, total;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    a = <span class=\"number\">10</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    b = <span class=\"number\">15</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    total = sum(a, b);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; total &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    system(<span class=\"string\">\"pause\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>其中m和n是形参，a和b是实参。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>函数的参数</p>\n<p>当调用函数时，有三种向函数传递参数的方式：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">调用类型</th>\n<th align=\"left\">描述</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">传值调用</td>\n<td align=\"left\">该方法将参数的实际值赋给函数的形式参数，这种情况下，修改函数内的形式参数对实际参数没有影响。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">指针调用</td>\n<td align=\"left\">该方法将参数的地址赋值给形式参数，地址用于在函数调用时访问实际参数，这种情况况下，修改函数内的形式参数会影响到实际参数。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">引用调用</td>\n<td align=\"left\">该方法把参数的引用赋值给形式参数，引用用于访问调用中要用到的实际参数，这种情况下，修改函数内的形式参数会影响到实际参数。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><strong>传值调用实例</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 函数定义</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">swap</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> y)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> temp;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp = x; <span class=\"comment\">/* 保存 x 的值 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    x = y;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 把 y 赋值给 x */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    y = temp; <span class=\"comment\">/* 把 x 赋值给 y */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 函数声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">swap</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> y)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 局部变量声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a = <span class=\"number\">100</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b = <span class=\"number\">200</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换前，a 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换前，b 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 调用函数来交换值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    swap(a, b);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换后，a 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换后，b 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    system(<span class=\"string\">\"pause\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>运行结果</p>\n<p><img src=\"/20202020/505/927/C++%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C1.jpg\" alt></p>\n<p><strong>指针调用实例</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 函数定义</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">swap</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>* x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>* y)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> temp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp = *x;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 保存地址 x 的值 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    *x = *y;        <span class=\"comment\">/* 把 y 赋值给 x */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    *y = temp;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 把 x 赋值给 y */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 函数声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">swap</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>* x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>* y)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 局部变量声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a = <span class=\"number\">100</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b = <span class=\"number\">200</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换前，a 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换前，b 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">/* 调用函数来交换值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">     * &amp;a 表示指向 a 的指针，即变量 a 的地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">     * &amp;b 表示指向 b 的指针，即变量 b 的地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">     */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    swap(&amp;a, &amp;b);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换后，a 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换后，b 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    system(<span class=\"string\">\"pause\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>运行结果</p>\n<p><img src=\"/20202020/505/927/C++%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C2.jpg\" alt></p>\n<p><strong>引用调用实例</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 函数定义</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">swap</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&amp; x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&amp; y)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> temp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    temp = x; <span class=\"comment\">/* 保存地址 x 的值 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    x = y;    <span class=\"comment\">/* 把 y 赋值给 x */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    y = temp; <span class=\"comment\">/* 把 x 赋值给 y  */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 函数声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">swap</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>* x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>* y)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 函数声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">swap</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&amp; x, <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>&amp; y)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 局部变量声明</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> a = <span class=\"number\">100</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> b = <span class=\"number\">200</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换前，a 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换前，b 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">/* 调用函数来交换值 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    swap(a, b);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换后，a 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; a &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class=\"string\">\"交换后，b 的值：\"</span> &lt;&lt; b &lt;&lt; <span class=\"built_in\">endl</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    system(<span class=\"string\">\"pause\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>运行结果</p>\n<p><img src=\"/20202020/505/927/C++%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C3.jpg\" alt></p>\n<p>指针传参和引用传参多用于函数返回值不止一个的情况，只要合理使用会给函数的使用带来不少方便。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","tags":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","permalink":"http://euansu123.github.io/tags/C/"}]},{"title":"live2d看板娘部署至hexo","date":"2020-05-09T15:10:12.000Z","path":"20202020/505/909/live2d看板娘部署至hexo/","content":"<h2 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h2><h3 id=\"安装live2d模块\"><a href=\"#安装live2d模块\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装live2d模块\"></a>安装live2d模块</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save hexo-helper-live2d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"选择自己喜欢的看板娘\"><a href=\"#选择自己喜欢的看板娘\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"选择自己喜欢的看板娘\"></a>选择自己喜欢的看板娘</h3><p>我自己使用的是<strong>mizuku</strong>。</p>\n<p><strong>Epsilon2.1</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/Epsilon2.1.gif\" alt=\"Epsilon2.1\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<p><strong>haru</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/haru.gif\" alt=\"haru\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>haruto</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/haruto.gif\" alt=\"haruto\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\">\n\n<p><strong>hibiki</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/hibiki.gif\" alt=\"hibiki\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>hijiki</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/hijiki.gif\" alt=\"hijiki\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\">\n\n<p><strong>koharu</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/koharu.gif\" alt=\"koharu\" style=\"zoom:67%;\">\n\n<p><strong>miku</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/miku.gif\" alt=\"miku\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>nico</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/nico.gif\" alt=\"nico\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>nietzche</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/nietzche.gif\" alt=\"nietzche\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>ni-j</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/ni-j.gif\" alt=\"ni-j\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>nipsilon</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/nipsilon.gif\" alt=\"nipsilon\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>nito</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/nito.gif\" alt=\"nito\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>shizuku</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/shizuku.gif\" alt=\"shizuku\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>tororo</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/tororo.gif\" alt=\"tororo\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>tsumiki</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/tsumiki.gif\" alt=\"tsumiki\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>Unitychan</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/Unitychan.gif\" alt=\"Unitychan\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\">\n\n<p><strong>wanko</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/wanko.gif\" alt=\"wanko\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p><strong>z16</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/live2d%E7%9C%8B%E6%9D%BF%E5%A8%98%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%B3hexo/z16.gif\" alt=\"z16\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<h3 id=\"安装看板娘\"><a href=\"#安装看板娘\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装看板娘\"></a>安装看板娘</h3><p>例如安装shizuku</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save live2d-widget-model-shizuku</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"修改配置文件\"><a href=\"#修改配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改配置文件\"></a>修改配置文件</h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># Live2D</span><br><span class=\"line\">## https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;xiazeyu&#x2F;live2d-widget.js</span><br><span class=\"line\">## https:&#x2F;&#x2F;l2dwidget.js.org&#x2F;docs&#x2F;class&#x2F;src&#x2F;index.js~L2Dwidget.html#instance-method-init</span><br><span class=\"line\">live2d:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  model:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scale: 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">    hHeadPos: 0.5</span><br><span class=\"line\">    vHeadPos: 0.618</span><br><span class=\"line\">    use: live2d-widget-model-shizuku #下载的看板娘名称</span><br><span class=\"line\">  display:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    superSample: 2</span><br><span class=\"line\">    width: 150</span><br><span class=\"line\">    height: 300</span><br><span class=\"line\">    position: right #展示位置</span><br><span class=\"line\">    hOffset: 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">    vOffset: -20</span><br><span class=\"line\">  mobile: #移动设备展示选择</span><br><span class=\"line\">    show: true</span><br><span class=\"line\">    scale: 0.5</span><br><span class=\"line\">  react:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    opacityDefault: 0.7</span><br><span class=\"line\">    opacityOnHover: 0.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"部署到hexo网站\"><a href=\"#部署到hexo网站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署到hexo网站\"></a>部署到hexo网站</h3><p>1、首先清空本地缓存</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>2、生成博客文件</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>3、启动服务器，本地测试修改</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>4、部署至hexo网站</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"卸载\"><a href=\"#卸载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"卸载\"></a>卸载</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm uninstall hexo-helper-live2d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","permalink":"http://euansu123.github.io/tags/hexo/"}]},{"title":"ESP分区装在机械硬盘的解决方案","date":"2020-05-09T12:37:00.000Z","path":"20202020/505/909/ESP分区装在机械硬盘的解决方案/","content":"<p>重装固态硬盘后，由于机械硬盘已经分区，因此机械硬盘变成首选项，所以系统的引导建立在了机械盘。</p>\n<p>作为一个强迫症患者，还是受不了系统在固态而引导在机械盘的问题，因此搜索了许多办法，最终发现这个问题早在16年就已经有解决的方案。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<p>方案一：拆掉机械硬盘重新安装操作系统（如果你动手能力够强，并且有工具是个不错的方法）。</p>\n<p>方案二：利用分区工具DiskGenius在固态硬盘分出&gt;300M的ESP分区，虽然是300MB但是在克隆ESP分区时我的电脑始终显大小不足，最后还是分配了800MB的分区（这里还是建议用300MB，如果不可以可以适当扩大分区大小）。（下图是已经将ESP分区移动至固态硬盘的截图）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/20202020/505/909/ESP%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E8%A3%85%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/1.png\" alt></p>\n<p>分区结束后，就可以利用DiskGenius的克隆分区功能。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/20202020/505/909/ESP%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E8%A3%85%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/2.png\" alt></p>\n<p>然后就是进行克隆的工作，将ESP分区克隆至固态盘提前分好的区。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/20202020/505/909/ESP%E5%88%86%E5%8C%BA%E8%A3%85%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%BA%E6%A2%B0%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/3.png\" alt></p>\n<p> 如果在DiskGenius显示如上图则说明ESP分区迁移成功。</p>\n<p>MSR分区的迁移方法同上。</p>\n","tags":[{"name":"随笔","slug":"随笔","permalink":"http://euansu123.github.io/tags/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/"}]},{"title":"信息安全基础","date":"2020-05-09T10:50:22.000Z","path":"20202020/505/909/信息安全基础/","content":"<h2 id=\"安全体系结构和模型（2课时）\"><a href=\"#安全体系结构和模型（2课时）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安全体系结构和模型（2课时）\"></a>安全体系结构和模型（2课时）</h2><p><strong>1、网络安全的核心目标：机密性、完整性、可用性。</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>机密性：对信息的访问和公开进行授权限制，包括保护个人隐私和私密信息，包括数据机密性（保证私有的或机密的信息不会被泄露给未经授权的个体）和隐私性（保证个人可控制和影响与之相关的那些信息是可以被收集、被保存的、这些信息可以有谁来公开以及向谁公开）。</li>\n<li>完整性：包含了数据完整性（保证只能由特定的，已授权的方式来更改信息和代码）和系统完整性（保证系统正常实现其预期功能，而不会被非授权操作控制）。</li>\n<li>可用性：确保系统能工作迅速，对授权用户不能拒绝服务。</li>\n</ul>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<p><strong>2、OSI安全体系结构：安全攻击（任何危机信息系统安全的行为）、安全机制（用来检测、阻止攻击或者从攻击状态恢复到正常状态的过程）、安全服务（为系统或数据传输提供足够安全的协议层服务）。</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>安全攻击：包括主动攻击（改写</li>\n<li>、伪造数据流；形式：假冒、重放、改写消息、拒绝服务；特点：难以预防；解决方案：检测+快速修复）和被动攻击（目标是获取传输的信息，本质是对传输进行窃听和监测；特点：很难察觉；解决方法：重点是预防，即通过加密的手段组织这种攻击）。</li>\n<li>安全服务：认证（确保通信实体就是它所声称的实体）、访问控制（防止对资源的非授权使用）、数据保密性（防止非授权的数据泄露）、数据完整性（确保授权实体发送的收据与接收到的数据完全相同，即无篡改、插入、删除或修改）、不可否认性（防止通信过程中任一通信实体进行否认的行为）。</li>\n<li>安全机制：包括特定的安全机制（可以并入到适当的协议层提供安全服务，主要方式：加密、数字签名、访问控制、数据完整性、认证交换、流量填充、路由控制、公证）和普通的安全机制（不局限于任何特定的OSI安全服务或协议层的机制，主要方式：可信功能、安全标签、事件检测、安全审计、跟踪安全恢复）。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>3、网络安全模型</strong></p>\n<img src=\"/20202020/505/909/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/1.png\" alt=\"网络安全模型\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n\n<p>网络安全技术的目的：加密（对待发送消息进行安全相关的变换）、数字签名（双方共享某些秘密信息）。</p>\n<h2 id=\"密码学\"><a href=\"#密码学\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"密码学\"></a>密码学</h2><h3 id=\"传统密码学\"><a href=\"#传统密码学\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"传统密码学\"></a>传统密码学</h3><p><img src=\"/20202020/505/909/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/2.png\" alt=\"传统密码的简化模型\"></p>\n<p>传统加密技术的组成：明文、密钥、加密算法、密文、解密算法。</p>\n<p>传统密码学的技术有：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>代替技术：将明文字符替换成其他字母、数字或者符号的方法。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>置换技术：对明文进行置换。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>转轮机：由三个转速的转轮构成，每次按键会改变快速转子上ABC..Z的顺序，多次按键之后会改变中速转子和慢速转子上的数字位置，因此整个转轮机有26 * 26 * 26=17576个不同的替换字母表。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"/20202020/505/909/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/3.png\" alt=\"三轮转轮机\" style=\"zoom:50%;\">\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>隐写术：也就是隐藏明文信息。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"现代密码学\"><a href=\"#现代密码学\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"现代密码学\"></a>现代密码学</h3><p><strong>1、对称加密算法</strong></p>\n<p>（1）对称加密算法的安全使用要求：需要有一个强加密算法：攻击者知道加密算法也不能破译或解出密钥；密钥安全：密钥传输安全、密钥存储安全。<br>（2）对称加密算法的数学表示：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>明文：P、密文：C、密钥：K。</li>\n<li>加密：C=E[P,K]=E[D[C,K],K]</li>\n<li>解密：P=D[C,K]</li>\n</ul>\n<p>（3）加密算法的选择（至少满足一条就认为是安全的）：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>破解密文的代价超过加密信息的价值。</li>\n<li>破解密文需要的时间超出信息的有效生命周期。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>（4）对称加密算法：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>数据加密标准DES</li>\n<li>三重数据加密标准3DES</li>\n<li>高级加密标准AES</li>\n</ul>\n","tags":[{"name":"信息安全","slug":"信息安全","permalink":"http://euansu123.github.io/tags/%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8/"}]}]